- Just say the address to the app and the navigation of Waze will start instantly ! (With no clicks at all).

- Street view of your destination which is not an option in Waze.
- Save your history and favorite Waze locations.
- Launch up to 3 favorite Waze locations from your “today widget”.

Electromaps enables you to find all available charging stations for electric vehicles, and to activate and pay for charging sessions. With Electromaps you can search for charging stations by speed of charging, connector type, power available, type of location - find the one that best suits your needs.

More than 500,000 charge points for your electric vehicle available in more than 200,000 locations!

ELECTROMAPS FEATURES

- find charging stations near your location or search for charging stations at your destination or in your route
- filter your charging station searches by speed of charging, connector type, location type, etc.
- check the real-time status of connected charging stations

A SINGLE APP FOR PAYMENTS THROUGHOUT EUROPE

Commuter is an app that helps you plan public transport journeys and find information easily about stops nation wide. 

Features include:
 ● Search for routes with easy search
 ● Search for stops by name, code or address
 ● See realtime locations of trams, metros and trains in the capital region
 ● Find stops from a map
 ● List nearby stops
 ● View either the departures from the stop in the near future or the full timetable.
 ● Set a reminder for a departure from a stop or time to leave for a route.
 ● Bookmark stops, routes and any address for easy access later. 
 ● Search for address from your contacts
 ● Departures widget for easy access to your saved stops and get departure times quickly. 
● Integrated with iOS Maps app for searching for transit options for a route opened in Maps.
